<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-02-0220 </DOCNO><TEXT>After a short introduction to digital image processing the applicationin the field of materials testing is discussed and some typical examplesare presented. The paper describes image processing methods like imageenhancement for visual inspection, quantitative image analysis and imageinterpretation. In detail the automatic image interpretation of weldradiographs is discussed and defect recognition, feature extraction anddefect classification are explained.</TEXT></DOC>